<p><a name="Critical_views" id="Critical_views"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Sun_Myung_Moon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=44" title="Edit section: Critical views">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Critical views</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.gorenfeld.net/book/" class="external text" title="http://www.gorenfeld.net/book/" rel="nofollow">Critical site by journalist John Gorenfeld</a>.</li>
<li><a href="http://video.aol.com/video-detail/nan-sook-hong/1354477572" class="external free" title="http://video.aol.com/video-detail/nan-sook-hong/1354477572" rel="nofollow">http://video.aol.com/video-detail/nan-sook-hong/1354477572</a></li>
</ul>
<p><a name="Mixed_views" id="Mixed_views"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Sun_Myung_Moon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=45" title="Edit section: Mixed views">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Mixed views</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.geocities.com/unificationism/" class="external text" title="http://www.geocities.com/unificationism/" rel="nofollow">An introduction to Unificationism (Sun Myung Moon's Unification Church)</a> including both support and criticism from current and former Unificationists.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.unification.org/ucbooks/earlyyears/" class="external text" title="http://www.unification.org/ucbooks/earlyyears/" rel="nofollow"><i>Sun Myung Moon, The Early Years, 1920-53</i></a>, unofficial biography by Michael Breen, a Seoul-based author and journalist.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.petermaass.com/core.cfm?p=1&amp;mag=48&amp;magtype=1" class="external text" title="http://www.petermaass.com/core.cfm?p=1&amp;mag=48&amp;magtype=1" rel="nofollow">Moon at Twilight</a>, 1998 <a href="/wiki/New_Yorker" title="New Yorker">New Yorker</a> article by <a href="/wiki/Peter_Maass" title="Peter Maass">Peter Maass</a> who interviewed church members in Asia and North and South America.</li>
</ul>
